That’s realistic.

00:11:29.019 --> 00:11:32.898 line:90% position:50% align:center
It acknowledges the fact
that sometimes we’re afraid,

00:11:32.898 --> 00:11:35.317 line:90% position:50% align:center
but it tells us what to do about it

00:11:35.317 --> 00:11:38.070 line:90% position:50% align:center
—to put our trust in Jehovah.

00:11:39.447 --> 00:11:44.452 line:90% position:50% align:center
Next year, we’ll have many opportunities
to meditate on that statement

00:11:44.452 --> 00:11:47.789 line:90% position:50% align:center
because the Governing Body has chosen it

00:11:47.789 --> 00:11:51.085 line:90% position:50% align:center
