00:11:51.085 --> 00:11:52.711 line:90% position:50% align:center
Once again,

00:11:52.711 --> 00:11:56.299 line:90% position:50% align:center
that’s Psalm 56:3:

00:11:56.299 --> 00:12:00.345 line:90% position:50% align:center
“When I am afraid, I put my trust in you.”

